data.description:
Nestled in Ridgefield neighborhood, , this spacious dwelling boasts 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, offering a plenty of space and functionality! Upon entering, the foyer sets the tone for a warm welcome. To the right, discover a seamlessly living space that gracefully flows into the formal dining area, creating an ideal setting for close gatherings! The heart of this home resides in its well-appointed kitchen, complete with an eat-in area, granite countertops, tile backsplash, and stainless steel appliances! Adjoining the kitchen, a spacious and inviting den awaits! Showcasing striking wood beams and a captivating stone fireplace, this den becomes a cozy retreat. Its built-in shelving adds functionality while sliding glass doors seamlessly merge indoor and outdoor living, leading to an expansive backyard—a haven for outdoor entertainment and relaxation! 
The allure continues with the choice of wood flooring in the bedrooms, adding a touch of natural warmth and timeless appeal. The main bedroom boasts not one but two closets, providing ample storage space and convenience! Don't miss your chance to make this your new home!
